    "name": "Tink Payments API",
    "description": "Tink Payments (Payment Initiation Service / Pay by Bank) initiates account-to-account payments directly from a customer's bank account under PSD2. Supports one-off domestic and cross-border SEPA payments, auto-payments, sweeping variable recurring payments, payouts, refunds, and mandates. Available in the EU under PSD2 and in the US via the Guaranteed Payments stack.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Tink Developer Support",
